'''Whitfoot''' was the [[Hobbits|Hobbit]] surname of [[Will Whitfoot]] and, presumably, any of his kin.<ref>{{FR|I9}}</ref>

Although they didn't seem to be of the upper class, they had some prominence as one of them was [[Mayor of Michel Delving]].<ref>{{HM|Guide}}, entry "Whitfoot"</ref>
==Etymology==
The name "Whitfoot" is derived from "White foot".<ref>{{HM|N}}</ref>
